If you're having trouble here is some further tips:
First create 3 Knights (k1,k2 and k3) at 3 different Spawns. Then add them to an Army like this:
Army knights = new Army(k1,k2,k3);

while(!(k3.targetsEntity())) {
	knights.wait();
}
And after that make all of them wait, move twice and then wait again.
